  "title": "ViewRef",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L11-L41\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts#L11-L41\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/ViewRef\", \"name\": \"ViewRef\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"viewref\">ViewRef<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#viewref\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Represents an Angular <a href=\"guide/glossary#view\">view</a>,\nspecifically the <a href=\"guide/glossary#view-tree\">host view</a> that is defined by a component.\nAlso serves as the base class\nthat adds destroy methods for <a href=\"guide/glossary#view-tree\">embedded views</a>.</p>\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\">\nabstract class <a href=\"api/core/ViewRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ViewRef</a> extends <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\">ChangeDetectorRef</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#destroyed\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">destroyed</span>: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#destroy\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">destroy</span>(): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#onDestroy\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">onDestroy</span>(callback: Function): any</a>\n\n  // inherited from <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\">core/ChangeDetectorRef</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#markForCheck\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">markForCheck</span>(): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#detach\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">detach</span>(): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#detectChanges\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">detectChanges</span>(): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#checkNoChanges\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">checkNoChanges</span>(): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#reattach\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">reattach</span>(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"descendants class\">\n    <h2 id=\"subclasses\">Subclasses<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#subclasses\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    \n\n<ul>\n  \n    <li>\n      <code><a href=\"api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">EmbeddedViewRef</a></code>\n      \n\n\n    </li>\n  \n</ul>\n\n\n  </div>\n  \n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">See also<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><p><code><a href=\"api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">EmbeddedViewRef</a></code></p>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"properties\">Properties<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>Property</th>\n        <th>Description</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"destroyed\"></a>\n          <code>abstract <span class=\"member-name\">destroyed</span>: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td><span class=\"read-only-property\">Read-only.</span>\n          <p>Reports whether this view has been destroyed.</p>\n\n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"destroy\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"destroy\">\n        destroy()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#destroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L23-L26\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts#L23-L26\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>Destroys this view and all of the data structures associated with it.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">destroy</span>(): void</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<p>There are no parameters.</p>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n    <a id=\"onDestroy\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"ondestroy\">\n        onDestroy()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ViewRef#ondestroy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L33-L40\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts#L33-L40\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"short-description\">\n        <p>A lifecycle hook that provides additional developer-defined cleanup\nfunctionality for views.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">abstract <span class=\"member-name\">onDestroy</span>(callback: Function): any</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-1\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table instance-method-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"instance-method-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>callback</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p>A handler function that cleans up developer-defined data\nassociated with a view. Called when the <code>destroy()</code> method is invoked.</p>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns-1\">Returns</h4>\n<p><code>any</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/ApplicationRef\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\n - api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\n - api/core/ViewContainerRef\n - guide/glossary\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#checkNoChanges\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#detach\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#detectChanges\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#markForCheck\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#reattach\n - api/core/EmbeddedViewRef\n - api/core/ViewRef#destroy\n - api/core/ViewRef#destroyed\n - api/core/ViewRef#methods\n - api/core/ViewRef#onDestroy\n - api/core/ViewRef#ondestroy\n - api/core/ViewRef#properties\n - api/core/ViewRef#see-also\n - api/core/ViewRef#subclasses\n - api/core/ViewRef#viewref\n - guide/glossary#view\n - guide/glossary#view-tree\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L11-L41\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L23-L26\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L33-L40\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts#L11-L41\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts#L23-L26\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/7.0.0/packages/core/src/linker/view_ref.ts#L33-L40\n-->"
